data.description: SELLER IS OFFERING $5,000 TOWARDS BUYERS 2-1 INTEREST RATE BUY DOWN WITH FULL PRICE OFFER - THIS COULD SAVE YOU $300 A MONTH YOUR FIRST YEAR ON YOUR MONTHLY MORTGAGE!!! ALSO, IF YOU USE PREFERRED LENDER THEY WILL WAIVE APPRAISAL FEE...Check out this adorable ranch style home that’s located in a cul-de-sac that offers 3 bedrooms, 2 full baths and an open concept! This home features an updated and modernized approach with open shelving in the kitchen, fun color on cabinetry, tile backsplash, shiplap detail in the bathroom and newer fixtures. In addition to the interior updates, this home also has an updated deck with a fully fenced in backyard, brand new carpet, new roof installed summer 2023 and all new Samsung black stainless steel kitchen appliances and an above ground pool.
